eya_def_tools.data_models.energy_assessment.EnergyAssessment
Energy assessment details and results.
Attributes: gross_energy_assessment (GrossEnergyAssessment): Details and results for the assessment of gross energy yield. plant_performance_assessment (PlantPerformanceAssessment): Plant performance loss assessment categories including results. net_energy_assessment (NetEnergyAssessment): Details and results for the assessment of net energy yield.

eya_def_tools.data_models.energy_assessment.GrossEnergyAssessment
Gross energy assessment details and results.
Attributes: process_description (AssessmentProcessDescription): Specification of the process used to calculate the gross EYA estimates. results (EnergyAssessmentResults): Gross EYA estimates.

eya_def_tools.data_models.energy_assessment.NetEnergyAssessment
Net energy assessment details and results.
Attributes: process_description (AssessmentProcessDescription): Specification of the process used to calculate the net EYA estimates. results (EnergyAssessmentResults): Net EYA predictions, including central estimates, overall uncertainties and results at different confidence levels.

eya_def_tools.data_models.plant_performance.PlantPerformanceAssessment
Plant performance loss assessment broken into categories.
Attributes: categories (list[PlantPerformanceCategory]): Plant performance loss assessment categories including results. results (PlantPerformanceResults): Overall plant performance loss assessment results.

eya_def_tools.data_models.energy_assessment.EnergyAssessmentResults
Energy assessment results.
Attributes: annual_energy_production (list[Result]): Annual energy production estimates in GWh.

eya_def_tools.data_models.process_description.AssessmentProcessDescription
Description of a process used in an energy yield assessment.
Attributes: label (str): Label or name of the process or model. description (str): Description of the assessment process or model. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the plant performance loss subcategory. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.plant_performance.PlantPerformanceCategory
Plant performance loss assessment category.
Attributes: label (PlantPerformanceCategoryLabel(StrEnum)): Label of the plant performance loss category. description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the plant performance loss category. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the plant performance loss category. Default is None. subcategories (list[PlantPerformanceSubcategory]): Plant performance loss assessment subcategories that fall under the category. The subcategory objects include details and results at the subcategory level. results (PlantPerformanceResults): Plant performance assessment category results.

eya_def_tools.data_models.plant_performance.PlantPerformanceResults
Plant performance loss assessment results.
Attributes: efficiency (list[Result]): Dimensionless plant performance efficiency (loss factor) results.

eya_def_tools.data_models.result.Result
Collection of results a quantity along specific dimensions.
Attributes: label (Optional[str]): Label of the results. Default is None. description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the result. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the result. Default is None. assessment_period (Optional[AssessmentPeriod(StrEnum)]): Period of or in time that has been assessed and for which the results are applicable. Default is None. dimensions (Optional[list[ResultsDimension(StrEnum)]]): Dimensions along which the results are binned (all result values in the same results object must have the same dimensions). Default is None. statistics (list[ResultStatistic]): List of result statistic objects that each include result values for a specific statistic type.

eya_def_tools.data_models.result.ResultStatistic
Result values for one specific statistic type.
Attributes: description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the result statistic. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the result statistic. Default is None. statistic_type (StatisticType(StrEnum)): Type of statistic in the results component. values (UnionType[float, list[tuple[list[UnionType[float, int, str]], float]]]): Result as a single number or values at coordinates.

eya_def_tools.data_models.plant_performance.PlantPerformanceSubcategory
Plant performance loss assessment subcategory.
Attributes: label (PlantPerformanceSubcategoryLabel(StrEnum)): Label of the plant performance loss subcategory. description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the plant performance loss subcategory. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the plant performance loss subcategory. Default is None. basis (AssessmentBasis(StrEnum)): Basis of plant performance loss subcategory assessment. The basis describes the level of detail of the calculation or estimate used in the assessment of the subcategory. variability (TimeVariabilityType(StrEnum)): Considered variability in the plant performance loss subcategory. assessment_process_descriptions (Optional[list[AssessmentProcessDescription]]): Description of calculation processes used in the assessment of the plant performance loss subcategory. Default is None. elements (Optional[list[PlantPerformanceSubcategoryElement]]): Plant performance loss assessment elements that fall under the subcategory. The element objects include details and results at the element level. A breakdown of plant performance loss subcategories into elements is optional and can be included only for a subset of the subcategories, as relevant. Whereas the categories and subcategories are fixed, the user may freely define element labels. Default is None. results (PlantPerformanceResults): Plant performance assessment subcategory results.

eya_def_tools.data_models.plant_performance.PlantPerformanceSubcategoryElement
Plant performance loss assessment subcategory element.
Attributes: label (str): Label of the plant performance loss subcategory element. description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the plant performance loss subcategory element. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the plant performance loss subcategory element. Default is None. basis (AssessmentBasis(StrEnum)): Basis of plant performance loss subcategory element assessment. The basis describes the level of detail of the calculation or estimate used in the assessment of the element. variability (TimeVariabilityType(StrEnum)): Considered variability in the plant performance loss subcategory element. is_independent (bool): Whether the plant performance loss subcategory element is independent of all other elements. Default is True. assessment_process_descriptions (Optional[list[AssessmentProcessDescription]]): Description of calculation processes used in the assessment of the plant performance loss subcategory element. Default is None. results (PlantPerformanceResults): Plant performance assessment subcategory element results.

eya_def_tools.data_models.scenario.Scenario
Single unique energy yield assessment scenario.
Attributes: id (Optional[str]): Optional unique identifier of the scenario. Default is None. label (str): Label of the scenario. description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the scenario. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the scenario. Default is None. is_main_scenario (Optional[bool]): Whether or not this is the main scenario in the report. Default is None. operational_lifetime_length_years (float): Number of years of project operational lifetime. wind_farms (list[WindFarmConfiguration]): List of all wind farms included in the scenario. turbine_wind_resource_assessment (TurbineWindResourceAssessment): Wind resource assessment at the turbine locations. energy_assessment (EnergyAssessment): Energy assessment details and results, including gross energy, plant performance, net energy and uncertainties.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_farm.WindFarmConfiguration
A collection of wind turbines considered as one unit (plant).
Attributes: id (str): Unique identifier of the wind farm. label (str): Label or name of the wind farm. abbreviation (Optional[str]): Optional abbreviated label of the wind farm. Default is None. description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the wind farm. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the wind farm. Default is None. turbines (list[TurbineConfiguration]): List of specifications for constituent turbines. relevance (WindFarmRelevance(StrEnum)): The relevance of the wind farm for the assessment ('internal', 'external' or 'future'). operational_lifetime_start_date (date): Operational lifetime start date of the wind farm (format YYYY-MM-DD). operational_lifetime_end_date (Optional[date]): Operational lifetime end date of the wind farm (format YYYY-MM-DD). Default is None. capacity (float): The total project capacity (in MW), which is the lesser of the maximum permanently transmittable power at the grid connection and the maximum production under typical conditions. restrictions (Optional[list[OperationalRestriction]]): List of operational restrictions at the wind farm level. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_resource.TurbineWindResourceAssessment
Wind resource assessment at the turbine locations.
Attributes: wind_resource_assessment_id_reference (str): The ID of the wind resource assessment on which the turbine wind resource assessment is based. This must refer to an ID of a wind resource assessment included at the top level of the EYA DEF. The schema requires that a turbine wind resource assessment is based on only one wind resource assessment. description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the turbine wind resource assessment. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the turbine wind resource assessment. Default is None. wind_spatial_modelling_processes (list[AssessmentProcessDescription]): Wind spatial modelling processes used in the assessment. results (TurbineWindResourceResults): Results of the wind resource assessment at the turbine location(s). wind_uncertainty_assessment (WindUncertaintyAssessment): Wind related uncertainty assessment categories including results.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_farm.OperationalRestriction
Specifications of a restriction that limits power output.
In the current draft of the schema, 'label', 'description' and 'comments' fields are available to describe the restriction with free text. This is intended to be expanded into a more comprehensive data model.
Attributes: label (str): Short label to indicate the type of operational restriction. description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the operational restriction. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the operational restriction. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_farm.TurbineConfiguration
Specification of all details for a turbine configuration.
Attributes: id (str): Unique identifier of the turbine. label (Optional[str]): Label of the turbine, if different from the 'id'. Default is None. description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the turbine. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the turbine. Default is None. location (Location): The horizontal spatial location of the turbine. ground_level_altitude (float): The ground level altitude (base elevation) of the turbine (in m). hub_height (float): The hub height of the turbine (in m). turbine_model_id (str): Unique identifier of the turbine model. operational_lifetime_start_date (Optional[date]): Operational lifetime start date of the individual turbine (format YYYY-MM-DD). Default is None. operational_lifetime_end_date (Optional[date]): Operational lifetime end date of the individual turbine (format YYYY-MM-DD). Default is None. restrictions (Optional[list[OperationalRestriction]]): List of operational restrictions at the turbine level. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_resource.TurbineWindResourceResults
Wind resource assessment results at turbine locations.
Attributes: wind_speed (list[Result]): Final long-term wind speed estimates at the turbine location(s) in metre per second. probability (Optional[list[Result]]): Final long-term probability distribution estimates at the turbine location(s), such as wind speed probability distributions or joint wind speed and direction frequency distributions, as dimensionless values. Default is None. turbulence_intensity (Optional[list[Result]]): Final long-term turbulence intensity estimates at the turbine location(s) as dimensionless values. Default is None. wind_shear_exponent (Optional[list[Result]]): Final long-term power law wind shear exponent estimates at the turbine location(s). Default is None. temperature (Optional[list[Result]]): Final long-term temperature estimates at the turbine location(s) in degree C. Default is None. air_density (Optional[list[Result]]): Final long-term air density estimates at the turbine location(s) in kilogram per cubic metre. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_uncertainty.WindUncertaintyAssessment
Wind related uncertainty assessment broken into categories.
Attributes: categories (list[WindUncertaintyCategory]): Wind related uncertainty assessment categories including results. results (UncertaintyResults): Overall wind related uncertainty assessment results.

eya_def_tools.data_models.spatial.Location
Specification of a horizontal location in space.
Attributes: x (float): Location x-coordinate (typically easing). y (float): Location y-coordinate (typically northing).

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_uncertainty.UncertaintyResults
Uncertainty assessment results.
Attributes: relative_wind_speed_uncertainty (Optional[list[Result]]): Uncertainty assessment results as dimensionless relative values expressed in terms of wind speed and calculated as the standard deviation of the wind speed uncertainty distribution divided by the mean wind speed. Default is None. relative_energy_uncertainty (Optional[list[Result]]): Uncertainty assessment results as dimensionless relative values expressed in terms of AEP (annual energy production) and calculated as the standard deviation of the energy uncertainty distribution divided by the net P50 (50% probability of exceedance level) AEP. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_uncertainty.WindUncertaintyCategory
Category of a wind related uncertainty assessment.
Attributes: label (WindUncertaintyCategoryLabel(StrEnum)): Label of the wind related uncertainty assessment category. description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the wind related uncertainty category. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the wind related uncertainty category. Default is None. subcategories (list[WindUncertaintySubcategory]): Wind related uncertainty assessment subcategories that fall under the category. The subcategory objects include details and results at the subcategory level. results (UncertaintyResults): Wind related uncertainty assessment category results.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_uncertainty.WindUncertaintySubcategory
Subcategory of a wind related uncertainty assessment.
Attributes: label (WindUncertaintySubcategoryLabel(StrEnum)): Label of the wind related uncertainty subcategory. description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the wind related uncertainty subcategory. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the wind related uncertainty subcategory. Default is None. elements (Optional[list[WindUncertaintySubcategoryElement]]): Wind related uncertainty assessment elements that fall under the subcategory. The element objects include details and results at the element level. A breakdown of wind related uncertainty subcategories into elements is optional and can be included only for a subset of the subcategories, as relevant. Whereas the categories and subcategories are fixed, the user may freely define element labels. Default is None. results (UncertaintyResults): Wind related uncertainty assessment subcategory results.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_uncertainty.WindUncertaintySubcategoryElement
Subcategory element of a wind related uncertainty assessment.
Attributes: label (str): Label of the wind related uncertainty subcategory element. description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the wind related uncertainty subcategory element. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the wind related uncertainty subcategory element. Default is None. results (UncertaintyResults): Wind related uncertainty assessment subcategory element results.
